Peter T. Slover 
Executive Compensation
As Chief Financial Officer at SOPHIRIS BIO INC, Peter T. Slover  made $1,077,846 in total compensation.  Of this total $322,355 was received as a salary, $295,596 was received as a bonus, $446,032 was received in stock options, $0 was awarded as stock and $13,863 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


