Peter T. Slover, CPA

Age : 42Public asset : 10,296 USDLinked companies :  Sophiris Bio Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Peter T. Slover, CPA, is Chief Financial Officer at Sophiris Bio, Inc. Mr. Slover was previously employed as Vice President-Finance & Operations by Anadys Pharmaceuticals, Inc. and Auditor by KPMG LLP.He received his undergraduate degree from Shippensburg University of Pennsylvania.



